DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.Id, T1.GroupingId, T4.value FixedCalendar, T5.value FixedFrequency, T6.value FixedConvention, T7.value FixedDayCounter, T8.value IndexName, T9.value FloatFrequency, T10.value SubPeriodsCouponType FROM ORE.dbo.ConventionsSwap T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar T4 ON T1.FixedCalendar = T4.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType T5 ON T1.FixedFrequency = T5.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T6 ON T1.FixedConvention = T6.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter T7 ON T1.FixedDayCounter = T7.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T8 ON T1.IndexName = T8.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType T9 ON T1.FloatFrequency = T9.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesSubPeriodsCouponType T10 ON T1.SubPeriodsCouponType = T10.value

field.name: *FixedCalendar
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedCalendar, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedFrequency
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedFrequency, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedDayCounter
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedDayCounter, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *IndexName
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value IndexName,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: FloatFrequency
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FloatFrequency, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: SubPeriodsCouponType
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value SubPeriodsCouponType,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesSubPeriodsCouponType !T! ORDER BY value
